21 def call_service(service_name, service_msg_type, *args):
22  service_timeout = 3
23  # Connect to service
24  rospy.wait_for_service(service_name, service_timeout)
25  # Call service
26  service = rospy.ServiceProxy(service_name, service_msg_type)
27  response = service(*args)
28  return response

55  def assertStatus(self, ret):
56  self.assertIsNotNone(ret, msg="Assert Status cannot operate on None ret")
57  self.assertTrue(ret.status > 0, msg="status : {} - message : {}".format(ret.status, ret.message))
58 
59  def assertNotStatus(self, ret):
60  self.assertIsNotNone(ret, msg="AssertNotStatus cannot operate on None ret")
61  self.assertTrue(ret.status < 0, msg="status : {} - message : {}".format(ret.status, ret.message))

64  def save_program(cls, name, code, description, allow_overwrite=False):
65  req = ManageProgramRequest()
66  req.cmd = ManageProgramRequest.SAVE
67  req.name = name
68  req.language = cls.language
69  req.code = code

72  return call_service('/niryo_robot_programs_manager/manage_program', ManageProgram, req)
